Module org.postgresql.pljava.internal
Package org.postgresql.pljava.jdbc

Class ReadOnlyResultSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.postgresql.pljava.jdbc.AbstractResultSet
      • org.postgresql.pljava.jdbc.ObjectResultSet
        • org.postgresql.pljava.jdbc.ReadOnlyResultSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, ResultSet, Wrapper
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ResultSetBase
    public abstract class ReadOnlyResultSet
extends ObjectResultSet
    Implements all methods that change the ResultSet in any way as methods that yield an UnsupportedFeatureException.
    Author:
    Thomas Hallgren
